; Test token default break in parse_reserved_word
; Exercise parsing of identifiers that start with reserved-word letters
; but aren't reserved words (e.g., 'total' starts with 't' but is not 'true')

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(total)\n"
$10.00
$0.00
end test
